# HR Zone Run [Running] (2026-03-11) @RPE 6
@ focus: Multi-zone progression

- Warmup 10min @Z1
- Run 10min @140bpm
- Run 10min @70% of max HR
- Run 5min @Z3
- Run 5km @4:30/km
  > Pick up the pace for the final 2km.
- Cooldown 10min @Z1

> Demonstrates all targeting methods: literal HR, % of max HR, zone, pace.
